---
title: Bangers and Mash with Thyme Gravy and Broiled Veggies
description: Get ready for a British invasion, but this time it’s with a fab four of sausage, tomatoes, zucchini, and potatoes. With shorter days and cooler temperatures ahead, we thought there was no better place to look for inspiration than across the pond—the Brits know a thing or two about gray skies and sweater weather, after all. It’s comfort food at its finest, although we couldn’t help throwing in some veggies to keep things fresh.
